# Estimating Bell Diagonal States with Separable Measurements

This repository contains the code required to reproduce the plots from the paper:

**Noah Kaufmann, Maria Quadeer, and David Elkouss, *Estimating Bell Diagonal States with Separable Measurements*, Physical Review A, 2025.**

---

## Repository Structure

```
.
├── functions/               # Helper functions for data generation, estimation, risk calculations, analysis
├── data_figure_2-3.py       # Creates the data for Figures 2 and 3
├── data_figure_2-3.npy      # Output file of data_figure_2-3.py
├── data_figure_4-5.py       # Creates the data for Figures 4 and 5
├── data_figure_4-5.npy      # Output file of data_figure_4-5.py
├── figure_2.py              # Generates Figure 2 from data_figure_2-3.npy
├── figure_2.pdf             # Output of figure_2.py
├── figure_3.py              # Generates Figure 3 from data_figure_2-3.npy
├── figure_3.pdf             # Output of figure_3.py
├── figure_4.py              # Generates Figure 4 from data_figure_4-5.npy
├── figure_4.pdf             # Output of figure_4.py
├── figure_5.py              # Generates Figure 5 from data_figure_4-5.npy
├── figure_5.pdf             # Output of figure_5.py
```

